  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>크라프트 + 합지 박스 주문</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bdc0e485-5340-44bd-9e72-5f891e63ee18\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9234f244-e50c-481e-a671-0082eb4bceef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9234f244-e50c-481e-a671-0082eb4bceef\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMjkw/MDAxNzU3MjE2OTY3MTEw.CHz7pFJmxtu4jo3HPQOO2eCR_zfGotaM1QFg0VWzFMMg.ypX2pBCWI4jM91cWYHy8JZ75NwjX_T8IQTTayORi7Kcg.JPEG/%ED%81%AC%EB%9D%BC%ED%94%84%ED%8A%B8_%EB%B0%B1%EC%83%89_%EA%B3%A8%ED%8C%90%EC%A7%801.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMjkw/MDAxNzU3MjE2OTY3MTEw.CHz7pFJmxtu4jo3HPQOO2eCR_zfGotaM1QFg0VWzFMMg.ypX2pBCWI4jM91cWYHy8JZ75NwjX_T8IQTTayORi7Kcg.JPEG/%ED%81%AC%EB%9D%BC%ED%94%84%ED%8A%B8_%EB%B0%B1%EC%83%89_%EA%B3%A8%ED%8C%90%EC%A7%801.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8591e766-83e9-4bfd-9bb6-eb7370a25659\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-8591e766-83e9-4bfd-9bb6-eb7370a25659\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMTg5/MDAxNzU3MjE2OTgyOTA0.aWtOzPm3J6ehfDq7LOJQMuExw9TjerX8JslypX7iMCcg.0JpTtHkiL2gtbYAPgMLDxqn_LZY6OrOkNoRoeJvszyYg.JPEG/%ED%81%AC%EB%9D%BC%ED%94%84%ED%8A%B8_%EB%B0%B1%EC%83%89_%EA%B3%A8%ED%8C%90%EC%A7%802.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMTg5/MDAxNzU3MjE2OTgyOTA0.aWtOzPm3J6ehfDq7LOJQMuExw9TjerX8JslypX7iMCcg.0JpTtHkiL2gtbYAPgMLDxqn_LZY6OrOkNoRoeJvszyYg.JPEG/%ED%81%AC%EB%9D%BC%ED%94%84%ED%8A%B8_%EB%B0%B1%EC%83%89_%EA%B3%A8%ED%8C%90%EC%A7%802.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">크라프트 + 골판지 합지 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">크라프트지에 골판지를 합지하는 박스는 가장 일반적인 박스 중에 하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee68079f-9e84-4622-acf8-51700f494899\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65877a2a-0e1c-4bd8-8b67-bc1c92e1a437\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-463b7112-9e1a-482d-95a6-79448d4ee891\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e8fa4d3-c897-45f4-9495-10f4b52a25a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">골판지에는 일반 편아트지를 합지하기고 하지만 크라프트지를 합지했을 때 가장 색상이 잘 어울립니다. 하지만 아트지는 모든 색상을 컬러로 인쇄할 때 잘 표현되는 반면에 크라프트지는 컬러 인쇄가 제한적입니다. 특히 색상이 진한 갈색의 크라프트 보드지의 경우 컬러 표현에 매우 제한적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd6a6221-4916-4290-a9ee-57c6c0be70d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2580b006-d0a7-48da-8bab-76e62f806302\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c21d256d-4e60-4ed6-b277-79f54e1c8e84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-613841f2-ef9b-48f4-a6d3-92ab5b33ea10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상이 옅은 크라프트지의 경우 (예를 들어 베이 크라프트) 단가가 비싸고 절수도 제한적이라 경제적이지 않은 측면이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01f3fb94-c640-4795-ab52-b5170ac78fff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f5e36955-2586-4304-9a51-846ba4ed8c4f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d74edf8f-03b2-4dba-9501-1e59ca5d77c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cea02bb2-65b5-40f2-bc12-a6f8bdb93773\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이럴 때 단순한 별색 몇 가지로만 표현하여 심플한 골판지 합지 박스를 디자인하여 만들어 보시기 바랍니다. 이런 색상 중에 가장 어울리는 색상은 아무래도 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1a518564-f2b6-4dec-9cda-946a9d2e2dd8\" style=\"color:#ffffff;background-color:#555555;\"><b>백색</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3501c1af-6579-4251-9e61-1be9892c5155\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-6bdc5210-81c8-4c50-bba6-7efef031c9dc\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-602f0330-25c5-445a-86cb-d89f436caea4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-061a19c9-56f0-4380-95c1-6afb7059a42e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b29d11e8-3d0d-4ec3-b414-0adcec81b173\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e07c335-5da9-4094-9c49-a3032fd20836\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0366deec-4c2f-499b-9fba-f70dc9c95f00\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>□ 크라프트지의 특징</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7819f017-a089-4f3b-b0ad-effd97679158\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-227ab981-c3c4-43d2-8b84-6e1239ba5486\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4e38782f-dea4-4f3f-99c1-3bb9854bb969\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2685a8c2-d46f-472f-8c46-75aad949a988\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>크라프트지는 일반적인 대중이 생각할 때 친환경이라고 생각하는 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0edc468a-bf9a-4c68-b74b-f20efb94a87c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의 대표적인 케이스입니다. 친환경 종이가 많이 나와있음에도 불구하고 일반인은 크라프트지가 제일 친환경적이라고 생각합니다. 그렇기 때문에 친환경 제품을 주로 취급하는 회사나 그 제품은 크라프트지로 패키지를 많이 만들고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56cbb155-147d-4c0e-a63d-94503ad73192\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d59f2d1-c536-42ae-9281-2fc3ad12ff88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cfce2e3f-7532-496d-b831-995af9515ba9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a784eefd-c648-41b5-9424-b6669445d6b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지를 잘 활용하면 복잡하지 않고 심플하게 패키지 표면 디자인을 완성시킬 수 있으며 몇 가지 색으로도 충분히 제품을 부각시키는데 가능할 만큼 매력적인 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-090e0571-e418-4a82-9e57-1bba1cefdca5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9649555-8d14-4a65-aea7-038aac0abcae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0fe0b65b-8cc9-4a44-ba78-8a72b97cf774\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-26a328df-0fec-4a7d-a8cc-88a8b04b11b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 일반적인 오프셋 백색 인쇄로는 표현이 어려워서 실크인쇄로 색상을 표현해야 잘 인쇄되는 특성이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71371ac7-a49e-4636-ba7e-2a97519c87da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f748cfcd-24d0-4a1e-bd7f-8b5afc4d1652\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45452174-30c7-4ec5-b7f4-4902683adc9c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2629c269-1260-4c96-a39c-bc6795a8e559\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇기 때문에 생산성 면에서 대량 주문 시 곤란할 수 있어서 단가적으로 비 경제적일 수 있고 또한 동영상에서 보듯이 하나하나 수작업으로 처리하는 측면이 강해서 소량 생산에 어울립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6245a586-adb6-4057-b3af-ac8c447f17ca\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4d42e6c0-a09f-480a-80de-bab5ace66da5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18dc68b3-f8dd-44c1-b2e4-9c92a4033967\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-18dc68b3-f8dd-44c1-b2e4-9c92a4033967\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMTcw/MDAxNzU3MjE4MTQ0NTkz.ip2Kpy_VpGuP6va6_aDAk_dS2TbNUGgQLMCw2N_cKvAg.71vm5702EochNLB_vNiuFDUuPFX039ipGbx2PRy2t40g.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_181328827_05.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfMTcw/MDAxNzU3MjE4MTQ0NTkz.ip2Kpy_VpGuP6va6_aDAk_dS2TbNUGgQLMCw2N_cKvAg.71vm5702EochNLB_vNiuFDUuPFX039ipGbx2PRy2t40g.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250801_181328827_05.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-361d56fb-4134-49c6-9e5c-b6170e92d0cf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-74300243-ae27-4399-8c7d-49280053acd2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c27ecde-4c11-4663-896d-405d7447fdea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지의 백색 인쇄는 일반 오프셋 인쇄로는 잘 표현되지 않을 수 있습니다. 다시 말씀드리지만 실크인쇄는 단가적으로는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d6d67d73-1cdb-405d-a09a-24fc59daebbd\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>비 경제적</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c19c2a92-db0d-4e67-8b93-ef87a10d2082\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이니 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc42d590-30a1-4b56-8680-1fd1d9cee396\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-13ac8914-9820-4f3f-80bc-371a96dafba0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71652f0b-88bf-4aee-b509-55384ffc1d12\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-20979774-b8b1-4cf3-857a-5a14c0b22991\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>크라프트지 + e 골판지 합지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-934f8285-6b88-4352-8ec2-fc4aa814f962\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1dbf7af-790c-4639-b9f6-e7966f498994\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4131f869-04c4-4c00-8046-e04b6e856cf1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da161bcc-0e53-41d2-a6c9-efcbb7bab7b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지와 골판지를 합지하면 두 종이의 색상이 비슷하여 이질감이 적습니다. 또한 외부와 내부의 구분이 잘 가지 않아 편안한 시각적 효과도 노릴 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09140de0-b8cb-4f88-b096-437d5081f77a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01a88384-84c8-4894-853d-d2e2800462ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c759cbf3-316f-4e8c-aa8d-da31f96b9bb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-177d245d-9591-4481-92b9-cc8984520297\" style=\"color:#555555;\">친환경에 재생지라는 특징이 있다 보니 환경 측면에서 여러 가지 제품의 이슈를 강조할 수 있어 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e80748df-906c-4942-b4c9-f1c6d849188e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fbc0492c-1eb9-4805-b5b5-53627c913db2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e9c9b99-8e20-4597-8965-ea5aa03c3aea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-84722a0e-f93d-4121-abc4-2b58b163a8f7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합지는 150g 미만의 종이를 붙이기 때문에 단점은 골판지의 골 무늬가 보일 수 있다는 단점이 있습니다. 두꺼운 150g을 합지하더라도 골판지의 골모양의 노출을 막을 길은 없습니다. 물론 세심히 보지 않는다면 일반 소비자는 잘 모르거나 넘어갈 수 있습니다. 이런 무늬 노출의 단점을 보안하기 위해 나온 것이 싸바리 박스입니다. 갱판지, 즉, 보루지는 골 모양이 없는 두꺼운 종이이기 때문에 합지를 해도 골 무늬가 노출되지 않습니다. 이 이야기는 다음에 한번 다루겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe3d6c35-0983-4081-9361-a9e39e165a0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7d8a0d4c-e367-4517-964a-65c7c8535d8a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a919eead-95bb-4c99-b10f-d6813c3938d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6d6a010e-a3a8-4165-b69d-e96c15b30fd7\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>크라프트지의 후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbfe15c0-e7ae-49a9-9529-004a0d1081d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4fde887-aa59-4f22-87a1-bb414315fcab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddbbbf5e-b562-4996-99f9-ba86e3b49780\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7eec19b2-a989-4274-9c7f-596e7c5b4479\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지와 골판지 합지하여 패키지를 만들 때는 후공정을 하지 않는 것이 일반적입니다. 크라프트지에 박인쇄가 잘 어울리지 않을 수 있고 형압이나 부분 코팅 등도 특별한 경우를 제외하고는 사용하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ea1ec22-7ec8-4ede-9908-37e777757cb8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0de0e9b-0ffa-4f2b-b0b1-16ec2291e681\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e65065f9-0117-4148-9b22-a94d8bb3c8ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f43be2ab-faff-4ea4-b28f-0c9cfb847ee5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 자연적인 느낌으로 처리하는 목적이 강하기 때문에 백색 등 별색인쇄를 제외하고는 다른 후공정은 거의 하는 것을 본 적이 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c4a8a06b-c6da-4547-85b2-8bb8821fb0ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-349ac3de-1ba4-4600-a8eb-d853dc7b418b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62db2f27-7eca-4454-88ed-454e135167c7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1309b6a4-a154-4e15-9452-e6bed61dfbf2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 고객님의 선택에 따라 박인쇄나 기타 후공정이 이루어질 수 있습니다. 또한 약간 접히고 꺾이는 부분의 방지를 위해 코팅처리도 일반적으로 진행하지만 크라프트지는 꺾임, 터짐이 노출되더라도 코팅을 진행하지 않는 것이 통상 작업 방법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72725d88-7946-4fc5-9a97-a0ee4c991056\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5860dfe1-8439-4f38-b009-61abfdf28780\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-059f5c05-313f-480d-83cd-bfae4e0510ac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0def3a13-d2c2-4fd3-8811-53d290e214ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다시 말해 크라프트지는 약간의 터짐을 감수하고서라도 친환경적인 부분을 강조하는 제품에 어울리는 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-717294cc-1c87-4639-aedb-5b5b1a0ae477\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d248ca6-68a2-4578-8dcb-5d1f6baf7c7b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f59c9446-d714-4cf6-bf81-7ce79707e1a6\" style=\"\">크라프트지가 어울리는 업종</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f9e7251-a919-4fb6-b207-311a6fed1637\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6dd59922-032b-43bd-91e5-d6af1902d7e5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0c7cf79-8426-421d-a420-2eeeb241ec25\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 친환경 제품을 주로 판매하는 기업 및 개인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-886292d1-eb5e-4648-863f-f8579d57539b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ef0353e1-474f-40df-b550-10806520dfc5\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08c42ab4-a4b5-4ba3-a4e1-5e4997439761\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21a6b064-88e3-4210-9640-6488abc0a10a\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 베이커리, 유기농 제품, 친환경 농가 제품을 생산하는 기업</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-180e2017-a36f-40fe-9cb7-5de5ec4439ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d405973a-1464-4c36-831d-378ffbd72ab2\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c36d52c4-6228-4658-b3c2-912235a66f08\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19642598-ea47-4ded-ab73-039b01f4dd8f\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 기업의 대표 이미지가 친환경이라는 브랜드에 어울리는 제품, 즉, 기업이 친환경을 선도하는 마케팅을 한다든지, 아니면 리사이클 제품이 모델링인 회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d183d39f-8dc6-4f21-a3de-319d53da990e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5cbb62c0-9ce5-4c08-9799-f3b6cb664095\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9feaf8f6-71bd-4486-889c-96a8c92f2def\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc53fa06-eb4d-43a7-9bcb-00ed3e0b3af4\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 해외 수출 규제에서 벗어나기 위해 친환경의 제품을 생산해야만 하는 업체</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3360422-826b-4a21-af36-9785eca3bff3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2d02751-fa0f-48c0-8124-433280837549\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-069975cc-910e-42e0-b5d3-b2602abe8023\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0367fe5-81b2-4b70-a569-ca04555e8409\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 관공서나 국가를 상대로 제공되는 나라장터 제품 중에 친환경이 경쟁에서 유리한 비딩을 할 수 있는 제품</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dad9c54c-879e-4774-978d-d4d3f9f9392d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-dad9c54c-879e-4774-978d-d4d3f9f9392d\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfNDcg/MDAxNzU3MjIyMTY3Mjg0.dY7VWyr1EUIpOjP6NeuQ45H2wwvfBjBAsTt5CfUZYIgg.SE-pWBFFUOGuQIWFV6WdyI3Q5gpgyrkcdSdznUgqJUUg.PNG/SE-dad9c54c-879e-4774-978d-d4d3f9f9392d.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3016\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2266\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfNDcg/MDAxNzU3MjIyMTY3Mjg0.dY7VWyr1EUIpOjP6NeuQ45H2wwvfBjBAsTt5CfUZYIgg.SE-pWBFFUOGuQIWFV6WdyI3Q5gpgyrkcdSdznUgqJUUg.PNG/SE-dad9c54c-879e-4774-978d-d4d3f9f9392d.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-674d3f31-1a91-4eef-b716-3389eeaeb536\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-674d3f31-1a91-4eef-b716-3389eeaeb536\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfNzAg/MDAxNzU3MjIyMjU1NDc3.pDRulLpuPo0RqSIkxXX1Erxv2CbemfakuBVyGAMqJYcg.9EbXw42lVY9IR5CyGbIXeSCtcvqXy1z8dWoNt6kTNacg.JPEG/SE-674d3f31-1a91-4eef-b716-3389eeaeb536.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2510\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3016\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MDdfNzAg/MDAxNzU3MjIyMjU1NDc3.pDRulLpuPo0RqSIkxXX1Erxv2CbemfakuBVyGAMqJYcg.9EbXw42lVY9IR5CyGbIXeSCtcvqXy1z8dWoNt6kTNacg.JPEG/SE-674d3f31-1a91-4eef-b716-3389eeaeb536.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca90acae-d0e8-4117-9f90-8b4e41f78c58\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-38fa99e2-46ef-44dc-a62a-5adcc4762091\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-57a9ff92-b632-4328-a17c-ec1f11a44420\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 직접 식재료를 담아 식자재와 표면이 맞닿아 포장재로 친환경 또는 FSC 마크가 필수인 제품</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7d50ad4f-1744-4270-b7d0-49b7f7152239\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca3858be-fb15-426a-9d4e-fdcccbd78244\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-578e0a82-de53-4dd3-b1e6-f2eee84a5d7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에게 문의하시면 패키지나 인쇄 전반의 궁금한 모든 사항을 이해하기 편하게 설명드립니다. 언제든 어느 시간이든 많은 전화 부탁드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223998547821#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
